│   ├── dao/            # CSVHandler (file I/O)
│   ├── controllers/    # AuthController, EmployeeController, ItemController, BillController
│   ├── ui/              # LoginFrame, AdminDashboard, EmployeeDashboard, dialogs
│   └── Main.java
└── README.md


